# Medium Article – Day 02

## Title:
How BubuVerse Designed a Tokenomics Model That Actually Rewards Players — Not Just Early Investors

## Summary:
In this article I explain how BubuVerse’s tokenomics model is built to reward active players, not just early adopters.  
The post dives into:  
- The role of Starlight Energy and how it converts to in-game value  
- The balance between NFT progression and token distribution  
- How the system encourages long-term participation through play, guild mission rewards, and strategic effort

